{"tid":2096463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得西甲爭冠冇睇頭？ 冇季叮噹馬頭","createTime":"2020-07-06T06:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T08:20:39.000Z","uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f464f77fcecff1382e8fc221fc127050a382245","tid":2096463,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"MSN 3季之後就開始係咁<br />\n季季都係馬體皇馬自爆 <br />\n<br />\n巴塞靠美斯單天保至尊<br />\n<br />\n今季馬德里正苦為咗罰加泰先畀12馬偷個冠返黎<br />\n<br />\n12馬同巴塞都冇統治力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ef0b30fb36e2f39123c97bb78e3d9f4a3cf3f5","tid":2096463,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"德甲FANS 如何是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f100f149a182e34b09f0ce3c1fba53ee556681","tid":2096463,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ef0b30fb36e2f39123c97bb78e3d9f4a3cf3f5","tid":2096463,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"德甲FANS 如何是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"意甲季初都話有啲睇頭<br />\n又係國米自爆 拉素依家開始自爆 <br />\n阿特蘭大入得多波但係分數追唔到上黎<br />\n益咗沙利攞冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce61aaa4cacd9efb3ed51ed9905e626d580a62b","tid":2096463,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"咁拜仁真係有統治力既 歐聯都睇好佢<br />\n拜仁同12馬相比差好遠喎 拜仁起碼都叫有實力 唔駛下下靠12碼贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上國家隊迫人轉會拜仁唔畀去英超 拜仁咁多人幫好難唔冠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636e2984d84cccd4e8dc0a354524248afaf7651a","tid":2096463,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ef0b30fb36e2f39123c97bb78e3d9f4a3cf3f5","tid":2096463,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"德甲FANS 如何是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"德甲今季ok 啦 拜仁試過排第七"},{"pid":"ff90361cf94c34bb78f772cbecf2cc49b6073d32","tid":2096463,"uid":40839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:16:33.000Z","msg":"今季巴塞唔爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放生巴塞都贏唔到皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtUJgeX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtUJgeX.jpg&h=c076ebab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBKMYti.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBKMYti.jpg&h=cd0f1763&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"168c8341dea078fff189161773e3d827a1ca4c00","tid":2096463,"uid":28858,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算贏巴塞?<br />\n1.要在巴塞顛峰期踢定勝負<br />\n2.要在巴塞內部沒有矛盾的時候踢<br />\n3.要在美斯狀態最好的時候踢<br />\n4.你不能往禁區起高球<br />\n5.你不能遠射進球<br />\n6.你不能防守反擊，你要全隊都攻出來<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給巴塞對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能擺鐵桶陣<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向巴塞，最好一開場就給主隊一張紅牌<br />\n10.美斯帶球，你不能幾個後衛去攔截，要讓美斯順利射門<br />\n11.你不能鏟美斯<br />\n12.你進的球前要把巴塞每個隊員都過一遍，最好把兩個門柱都過一遍，然後再把球踢進大門，這樣才是真水平，否則巴塞認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.你後衛在本方禁區不能開大腳<br />\n14.你要允許巴塞的教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">15.如該賽季非巴塞奪冠=西班牙政府懲罰加泰隆尼亞</span><br />\n16.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，巴塞迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。巴塞迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。<br />\n<br />\n又加多條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f005bab99e550cea3714664499ca71f1ffd5cca5","tid":2096463,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"鬧到32,33週先開始明朗 算係咁啦<br />\n唔通真係下下好似0607咁鬥對賽成績咩"}]}